										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">
<html><body><ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Visit the <a href="https://baoanhpro.vip/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">baoanhpro.vip</a> to see the website.</li>



<li>Take a look at the <a href="https://github.com/vanghoa/new-est-website" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">github repository</a>.</li>
</ul>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full span2" style="--width:3530; --height:1894;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="3530" height="1894" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4.png" alt="" class="wp-image-523" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4.png 3530w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4-300x161.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4-1024x549.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4-768x412.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4-1536x824.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps4-2048x1099.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 3530px) 100vw, 3530px" fetchpriority="high"></figure>



<p class="row2md">While working on this, I have looked into a lot of other personal website references from my friends and people I&nbsp;know on the Internet:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.rachelyeeunkim.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Rachel Yeeun Kim</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://kayserifserif.place/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Katherine Yang</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.themainwork.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mai Nguyen</a>, and countless other sources but those 3 are the&nbsp;main&nbsp;influences with a twist of my personality.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized" style="--width:1024; --height:549;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="549" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps5-1024x549.png" alt="" class="wp-image-524" style="width:659px;height:auto" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps5-1024x549.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps5-300x161.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps5-768x412.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps5-1536x824.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ps5-2048x1099.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" fetchpriority="high"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:579;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-525" style="object-fit:cover" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/internet-gems-rachel-yeeun-kim2-1024x579.jpg" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/internet-gems-rachel-yeeun-kim2-1024x579.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/internet-gems-rachel-yeeun-kim2-300x170.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/internet-gems-rachel-yeeun-kim2-768x434.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/internet-gems-rachel-yeeun-kim2.jpg 1432w"></figure>



<p class="row2">Ascii-ish stylized frames and decorative web elements sprinkled here and there.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:602;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="602" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-530" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr3-1024x602.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr3-1024x602.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr3-300x176.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr3-768x451.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr3-1536x902.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr3-2048x1203.png 2048w"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:625;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="625" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-529" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr1-1024x625.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr1-1024x625.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr1-300x183.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr1-768x469.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr1-1536x938.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr1-2048x1250.png 2048w"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:602;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="602" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-528" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr4-1024x602.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr4-1024x602.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr4-300x176.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr4-768x451.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr4-1536x902.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr4-2048x1203.png 2048w"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:602;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="602" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-527" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr2-1024x602.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr2-1024x602.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr2-300x176.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr2-768x451.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr2-1536x902.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr2-2048x1203.png 2048w"></figure>



<p>Another subtle concept is playing around with the text-highlighting/user-select interaction to reveal hidden messages.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:804; --height:1000;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:640; --theight:796;" alt="thumbnail" src="" data-src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1947113516-edce2372220c0f9d5b502a3e215d1bffa26d20b4ac39166bc51adfe2913a2254-d_640" data-srcset="" srcset=""><iframe title="Personal Website 2023 - Highlighting text" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1027192852?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large span2md" style="--width:1024; --height:613;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="613" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-538" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/hili-1024x613.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/hili-1024x613.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/hili-300x180.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/hili-768x460.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/hili.png 1530w"></figure>



<p class="row2md">To tribute my previous website in 2022, I put its front-end in the rear (in terms of Z axis), which can only reveal itself via the button <strong>&ldquo;&rsquo;-&hellip;__&hellip;-&lsquo;&ldquo;</strong>. The place also acts as a holder for my &lsquo;Guestbook&rsquo; function, in which visitors can leave messages for me directly on the site.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:741;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="741" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-536" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src7-1024x741.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src7-1024x741.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src7-300x217.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src7-768x555.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src7-1536x1111.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src7-2048x1481.png 2048w"></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="--width:1024; --height:602;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="602" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-532" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr5-1024x602.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr5-1024x602.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr5-300x176.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr5-768x451.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr5-1536x902.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/scr5-2048x1203.png 2048w"></figure>



<p>The initial conceptual idea of the site can be observed via the&nbsp;3D View&nbsp;of the developer tool of Microsoft Edge. Inspect the site to see.<br><br>Using a mix of &lsquo;z-index&rsquo; and &lsquo;transform-style: preserve-3d&rsquo; property, all the layers are arranged in a way that looks like a 3D sculpture when observed through the 3D View tool. This idea is to look at a website from a third-person perspective instead of the usual front-back view.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo span2"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:960; --height:510;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:960; --theight:510;" alt="thumbnail" src="" data-src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1947091424-31c0bc1f18d6fad71f72ae6b21f70a02d2281bec083c8e6c0c235dc1c693a07f-d_960" data-srcset="" srcset=""><iframe title="Personal Website 2023 - 3D layer view" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1027173378?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>A special section to attribute to those crossing paths with me in work throughout the previous years.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large span12" style="--width:1024; --height:768;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-540" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cre-1024x768.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cre-1024x768.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cre-300x225.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cre-768x576.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cre-1536x1152.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cre-2048x1536.png 2048w"></figure>



<p>Under the hood, I used Notion as the CMS backend to update everything on the site. You can view the database on Notion here&nbsp;<a href="https://prickle-robe-9ad.notion.site/B-o-Anh-s-personal-website-database-74c4132872904ed9855e05567cb116c3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">notion link</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full span2" style="--width:3546; --height:1882;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="3546" height="1882" src="" alt="" class="wp-image-535" srcset="" sizes="(max-width: 3546px) 100vw, 3546px" data-src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6.png" data-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6.png 3546w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6-300x159.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6-1024x543.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6-768x408.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6-1536x815.png 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2024/11/src6-2048x1087.png 2048w"></figure>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Site is built on&nbsp;Next.js&nbsp;with&nbsp;Tailwind CSS. CMS is from&nbsp;Notion</li>



<li>API&nbsp;with&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/9gustin/react-notion-render" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">react-notion-render</a> by @9gustin for data rendering and&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/guillermodlpa/upload-notion-images-to-cloudinary" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">upload-notion-images-to-cloudinary</a> by @guillermodlpa for hosting images form Notion to Cloudinary. Other dependencies include&nbsp;Prisma + PostgreSQL,&nbsp;Framer Motion,&nbsp;probe-image-size,&nbsp;seedrandom,&nbsp;react-lazy-load, &hellip; See the Github repository of the site here&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/vanghoa/new-est-website" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">github link</a>.</li>



<li>Typeface is&nbsp;<a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Alegreya" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Alegreya</a> designed by Juan Pablo del Peral, Huerta Tipogr&aacute;fica. Mono typeface is&nbsp;<a href="https://michaeljmcmaster.com/selectmono" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Select Mono</a> designed by MICHAEL McMASTER.</li>
</ul>
</body></html>
